text: Liparis goodyeroides is a species of plant in the family Orchidaceae. It is found in Cameroon and Nigeria. Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical dry forests. It is threatened by habitat loss. == Sources == * goodyeroides Category:Orchids of Cameroon Category:Orchids of Nigeria Category:Critically endangered plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
